»CL9:                                                          introduction
»CL8:                                                          ------------
»CL0:        party  time  is coming!  third time in a row astrodyn staff is
so  proud  to  announce  most  important  polish demoscene event named
[astrosyn`3]  or  [astrosyn`2000]  if you only want.  everything seems
like  last  astrosyn  was  a great success.  not so much attenders but
reall  great  productions  for amiga and pc - do it again, pals!  this
file is just simply announce.  if you want to know more details - read
forthcomming  versions  of it (always watch the release date, please).
READ THE RULES CAREFULLY and support this event again...  if you don`t
know  how  looks polish parties please ask satellite`99 attenders from
spain,  czech  or  holland.  astrosyn`3 will be really better and much
more "polish" in style =)
                            »PIC:Malmis4.128x50»


























»CL9:                                          when and where?
»CL8:                                          ---------------
»CL0:        ASTROSYN  2  will  be held as always in koszalin, »PIC:EC39.128x64»
northwestern poland  on  second or third weekend of march
2000. final  date  will  be published  in   the  official
invitation  at  the  beginning  of  new millennium.
partyplace  will  be  a  student club  named "kreslarnia"
(property  of  technical  uniwersity  of  koszalin, too).
not so huge place but fullfilled by great  atmosphere and
huge sound aparature.






























»CL9:                                                         general rules
»CL8:                                                         -------------
»CL1:-»CL0: entrance fee don`t grow up = 25 plz (~7 usd or ~12 dem). foreigners
  and nice girls comes for free as always. if you plane to take your
  computer with you we`ll honour you in special surprise competitions;

»CL8:-»CL0: no drugs are allowed at partyplace! it`s scene plague (mainly
  polish) and we don`t accept it, so use your weed or speed out of the
  party, please...

»CL8:-»CL0: alcohol is ALLOWED at the partyplace. you can drink everything and
  everywhere, but you can womit only at signed places =)

»CL8:-»CL0: we take no responsibility for any unregistered, uncensored or
  illegal software or hardware at the partyplce.

»CL8:-»CL0: if you crash something you`ll buy for it. you must to respect polish
  laws at the party place;






















»CL8:-»CL0: we don`t accept selling anything without our permission at the
  partyplace. there`s no obiections - just please ask us for it
  before, ok?

»CL8:-»CL0: no dance/disco music listeners environment are allowed at the
  partyplace. it`s not the discotheque! if we find someone who wear
  adibas dress we will kick his stupid ass and throw him up from the
  club. no respect for puny people like them...

»CL8:-»CL0: also if you want to spend party playing "quake" please stay at home.
  it`s demoscene and party is mainly place for real scenes, not lame
  gamers.  it`s not assembly or the gathering...




























»CL9:                                                          competitions
»CL8:                                                          ------------
-»CL0: we will continue the good idea - all the foreigners who want to
  contribute any compo mustn`t be present at the partyplace.  if you
  want to show something and compete with others but you can`t arrive
  here - just send it to us by snailmail or e-mail.  (take a look at
  addressess section for details) also www service will be available
  from the december`99.

»CL8:-»CL0: selection will be done only in music competitions.  there`s no
  reason to do it in other kind of compos, so all the stuff sended to
  us will be shown on the bigscreen.  the only shame for shitty
  productions must go to the authors...

»CL8:-»CL0: iformations about the compo machines will be published in official
  invitation.
























