»CL8:-»CL0: max. two productions for one coder;
»CL8:-»CL0: quit by pressing [lpm] or [esc] in every moment!;
»CL8:-»CL0: for pc: no sound support please!;























»CL0:                     amiga / pc 4kb intro compo:

»CL8:-»CL0: not bigger than 4kb in one file (4,096 bytes);
»CL8:-»CL0: not longer than 10 minutes please;
»CL8:-»CL0: max. two productions for one coder;
»CL8:-»CL0: quit by pressing [lpm] or [esc] in every moment!;
»CL8:-»CL0: for pc: no sound support please!;

»CL0:                        4 channel music compo:

»CL8:-»CL0: no size limitations (try more than 2mb =);
»CL8:-»CL0: one module for one author;
»CL8:-»CL0: just first 3 minutes of tune will be played;
»CL8:-»CL0: protracker (mod.) format only!;
»CL8:-»CL0: conversions of commercal hits will be disqualified!;
»CL8:-»CL0: max. 15 tunes will be played to the audience;
»CL8:-»CL0: tunes will be played by using newest version of hippoplayer (amiga);























»CL0:                      multichannel music compo:

»CL8:-»CL0: no size limitations (no excesses please!);
»CL8:-»CL0: no more than 32 channels!;
»CL8:-»CL0: if you want - crunch your files by using xpk, lha, lzx, rar or zip;
»CL8:-»CL0: one module for one author;
»CL8:-»CL0: just first 3 minutes of tune will be played;
»CL8:-»CL0: mod, dbm, xm or s3m format only!;
»CL8:-»CL0: conversions of commercal hits will be disqualified!;
»CL8:-»CL0: max. 15 tunes will be played to the audience;

»CL0:                           mp3 music compo:

»CL8:-»CL0: tunes compressed in mp3 format (stereo, max 160bps);
»CL8:-»CL0: one module for one author;
»CL8:-»CL0: just first 3 minutes of tune will be played;
»CL8:-»CL0: conversions of commercal hits will be disqualified!;
»CL8:-»CL0: time limited to 4 minutes (size!);
»CL8:-»CL0: max. 10 tunes will be played to the audience;





















»CL0:                        8 bit graphics compo:

»CL8:-»CL0: pixelled graphics with max. 256 colors used;
»CL8:-»CL0: one picture for one author;
»CL8:-»CL0: max. resolution is 640x512. please do not use med-resolutions like
  640x256 and 320x512;
»CL8:-»CL0: formats: iff, gif, png - no others please;
»CL8:-»CL0: if you want - crunch your files by using xpk, lha, lzx, rar or zip;
»CL8:-»CL0: absolutely no selection - every entries which fullfill the compo
  rules will be shown to the audience;
              »PIC:OldPeasant.336x80»





























